X_mds = cmdscale(dist(Z, method = "minkowski", p = 2))

perp = 30
trans_tsne = tsne(Z, perp)
X_tsne = py_to_r(trans_tsne)

trans_umap = umap(Z, method = 'umap-learn', n_neighbors = 30, n_components = q)
X_umap = trans_umap$layout

plot(X_mds)

plot(X_tsne)

plot(X_umap)

grid.arrange(p_trust_kpca, p_trust_tsne, p_trust_umap,
             p_cont_kpca, p_cont_tsne, p_cont_umap,
             p_prec_kpca, p_prec_tsne, p_prec_umap,
             p_stress_kpca, p_stress_tsne, p_stress_umap,
             p_cor_kpca, p_cor_tsne, p_cor_umap,
             ncol = 3)

dat = data.frame(trust = c(og_errors_kpca[,1] - risks_kpca[,1], og_errors_tsne[,1] - risks_tsne[,1], og_errors_umap[,1] - risks_umap[,1]),
               cont = c(og_errors_kpca[,2] - risks_kpca[,2], og_errors_tsne[,2] - risks_tsne[,2], og_errors_umap[,2] - risks_umap[,2]),
               prec = c(og_errors_kpca[,3] - risks_kpca[,3], og_errors_tsne[,3] - risks_tsne[,3], og_errors_umap[,3] - risks_umap[,3]),
               dist_cor = c(og_errors_kpca[,5] - risks_kpca[,5], og_errors_tsne[,5] - risks_tsne[,5], og_errors_umap[,5] - risks_umap[,5]),
               type = c(rep("kPCA", 40), rep("t-SNE", 40), rep("UMAP", 40)))

ggplot(dat, aes(x = trust)) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "kPCA"), color = "red", fill = "red", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "t-SNE"), color = "green", fill = "green", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "UMAP"), color = "blue", fill = "blue", alpha = 0.3)

ggplot(dat, aes(x = cont)) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "kPCA"), color = "red", fill = "red", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "t-SNE"), color = "green", fill = "green", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "UMAP"), color = "blue", fill = "blue", alpha = 0.3)

ggplot(dat, aes(x = prec)) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "kPCA"), color = "red", fill = "red", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "t-SNE"), color = "green", fill = "green", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "UMAP"), color = "blue", fill = "blue", alpha = 0.3)

ggplot(dat, aes(x = dist_cor)) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "kPCA"), color = "red", fill = "red", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "t-SNE"), color = "green", fill = "green", alpha = 0.3) +
  geom_density(data = subset(dat, type == "UMAP"), color = "blue", fill = "blue", alpha = 0.3)
